    "title": "Front Office Manager - The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Grow your career with The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Jabalpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited:\nThe Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited!",
